item.title: About
item.description: My name is Owen Smith, I build software leveraging machine learning and artificial intellegence. I’m facinated about how computers learn and how we can leverage their power to solve real world problems. I am currently based in Toronto, Canada. I study Computer Science at McGill University in Montreal, Canada and will be graduating at the end of 2021. In my spare time, I’m always working on side projects or learning about the latest frameworks and technologies.
